Sentencas: NiFe2O4 spinel coating is promising for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) steel interconnects application.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel

Sentencas: In this work, NiFe2 alloy coating was sputtered on bare steel and preoxidized steel (100 h in air at 800 degrees C), respectively, followed by exposing in air at 800 degrees C for up to 15 weeks in order to investigate the influence of steel preoxidation on high temperature behaviors of the coated steels.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel

Sentencas: The results indicated that an outer NiFe2O4 spinel layer atop an inner Cr2O3 layer formed on the coated samples after oxidation.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel

Sentencas: The preoxidation enhanced the oxidation resistance of the coated sample and reduced Cr out-migration to NiFe2O4 spinel layer.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel

Sentencas: After 15 weeks, the area specific resistance (ASR) of surface scale on the coated preoxidized steel was much lower than that on the coated bare steel.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel

Sentencas: The mechanisms of the preoxidation influence on oxidation behavior and surface scale electrical property of the coated steels were discussed.
Titulo: Influence of preoxidation on high temperature behavior of NiFe2 coated SOFC interconnect steel
